Capture and validate portability requests 1)Microservice: PortabilityRequestService Controllers: 1. PortabilityRequestController POST/requests → Capture new portability request GET /requests/{id} → View request details 2. ValidationController POST /requests/validate → Validate subscriber data against rules Services: 1. PortabilityRequestManager Create request entry in DB Generate unique request reference ID 2. ValidationService Check if MSISDN exists in DB Validate IMSI format Check ID type & number format 3. Provider LookupService Identify current & target provider IDs Models/Entities: PortabilityRequest Subscriber Provider
